article_title: Guess who's coming to lunch? The prez
article_text:
THIS BROWSER HAS SURPASSED NINE LIVES.

UPDATE SO YOU CAN SEE OUR SITE IN ALL ITS GLORY!

article_metadata.description: You've been working hard to spread the word about Obamacare and get people to sign up. Then one day, you get a call from the White House inviting you out to lunch. The purpose: a meet 'n greet with a super-important White House official who wants to chat with YOU about the affordable health care act.  After thinking about it for exactly one nanosecond, you hastily accept the offer -- who wouldn't?!
article_metadata.author: HLN Staff
